nodes.text: This unidentified Whiphid was a member of the Erased in 18 BBY, along with Dexter Jettster. In an unneccesary entanglement with Ferus Olin and Trever Flume he threw them around with his rather large tusks. After Dex smoothed things out and the rest of the Erased went searching for Solace, he stayed in the bar the Erased roamed in.
